Ay imeɣban yennumen, yennumen ṣṣber d tuggdi.
Tetten deg ufus n medden, ayen i d-ḥellan s tidi.
Tidi tenǧeṛ-d igeḍman, yeṭṭef-iten ufus anekkaṛ.
Afus-nni i ten-yerran, d igujilen s yiččumar.
Ay igujilen n yiles, a tagmat n yizamaren.
Anwa i d-yusan ar ad ten-yelles, s usemmiḍ kan i ḥulfen.
Ṛṛay mačči d ayla-nsen, ayagi d ayla n umeksa.
Nutni d acu ttalasen, siwa leḥcic ma yella.
Agellil n yigellilen, d win iɣef teḍsa tidi-s.
Tettmer ɣer wanda i tt-εelfen, widak yesqeḍn amur-is.
Agujil n yigujilen, d win yettewwten ɣer yiles.
Tiyita-nni i t-yessawḍen ɣ.er tidderɣelt ur ntekkes.
